text.en:
Activate 1 of these effects (but you can only use each effect of "Infernal Punisher" once per turn);
● Add 1 WATER Dinosaur monster from your Deck to your hand, then if your opponent controls a monster, you can Special Summon the added monster.
● Tribute 1 monster; Special Summon 1 Level 6 or higher FIRE monster from your hand, Deck, or GY, but if you Special Summoned a non-Fiend monster by this effect, negate its effects.
